" Help - Terminal and Split Management
" ============================================================================
"
" Terminal Scrolling:
"   When in Claude terminal, press Esc Esc to enter Normal mode
"   Then you can:
"     - Use j/k or arrow keys to scroll
"     - Use Ctrl-u/Ctrl-d for page up/down
"     - Use gg/G to go to top/bottom
"     - Use / to search
